data.description: Come take a look at this oversized TWO FAMILY HOME consisting of TWO Bedrooms, 1 full bath, washer and dryer hookups in the first floor and 3 bedrooms, one full bath, washer and dryer hookups for the second unit, and the option of extra living or storage space on 3rd floor! Features both front and back porches; hardwood floors throughout, replacement windows, circuit breakers, new tankless heat system and hot water,  a very sizable backyard, and parking for FOUR cars.
